CreatePositionCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> CreatePositionResource : transforms
CreatePositionCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> CreatePositionCommand : creates
CreateProductCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> CreateProductResource : transforms
CreateProductCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> CreateProductCommand : creates
CreateVehicleCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> CreateVehicleResource : transforms
CreateVehicleCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> CreateVehicleCommand : creates
CreateWarehouseCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> CreateWarehouseResource : transforms
CreateWarehouseCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> CreateWarehouseCommand : creates

EmployeeResourceFromEntityAssembler ..> Employee : transforms
EmployeeResourceFromEntityAssembler ..> EmployeeResource : creates
PositionResourceFromEntityAssembler ..> Position : transforms
PositionResourceFromEntityAssembler ..> PositionResource : creates
ProductResourceFromEntityAssembler ..> Product : transforms
ProductResourceFromEntityAssembler ..> ProductResource : creates
VehicleResourceFromEntityAssembler ..> Vehicle : transforms
VehicleResourceFromEntityAssembler ..> VehicleResource : creates
WarehouseResourceFromEntityAssembler ..> Warehouse : transforms
WarehouseResourceFromEntityAssembler ..> WarehouseResource : creates

UpdateEmployeeInfoCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> UpdateEmployeeResource : transforms
UpdateEmployeeInfoCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> ChangeEmployeePositionCommand : creates
UpdateEmployeeInfoCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> UpdateEmployeeStatusCommand : creates
UpdatePositionNameCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> UpdatePositionResource : transforms
UpdatePositionNameCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> UpdatePositionNameCommand : creates
UpdateProductInfoCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> UpdateProductResource : transforms
UpdateProductInfoCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> UpdateProductInfoCommand : creates
UpdateVehicleInfoCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> UpdateVehicleResource : transforms
UpdateVehicleInfoCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> UpdateVehicleInfoCommand : creates
UpdateWarehouseInfoCommandFromResourceAssembler ..> UpdateWarehouseResource : transforms
